{"tid":1138710,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我鐘意既人今日同我分享佢鐘意既人既野","createTime":"2019-05-04T17:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T04:49:40.000Z","uid":33153,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"391f6ea8d7593028434fbc4f324e73b4986f5bf2","tid":1138710,"uid":33153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:02:15.000Z","msg":"雖然係我衰多口問先<br />\n但知道佢有對象 有行動嗰一刻<br />\n都係好唔開心<br />\n同一個朋友講 佢話<br />\n其實人地friend zone左你先同你分享到呢啲野<br />\n啱吖 我都應該慶幸佢當我係好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問點樣先可以極速死心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7eb8464069dbcec5b151c7ecf509c5cd3676e9d","tid":1138710,"uid":58867,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:04:13.000Z","msg":"咁樣都死唔到心？"},{"pid":"dd1563e92f4e926813872bce2c0c4bdda215e355","tid":1138710,"uid":20448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:05:33.000Z","msg":"咁人地鍾意女人都好正常啊"},{"pid":"2d74d4c1d06cb30c433f2d10697103c70590bc57","tid":1138710,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:07:10.000Z","msg":"Let it go let it go"},{"pid":"53599590342d6ccfe530b4faa465f45986c108ed","tid":1138710,"uid":141237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:09:08.000Z","msg":"極速死心就係即刻斷絕聯繫，del records<br />\ndel晒所有可以contact到既途徑。<br />\n<br />\n依段時間，你會好糾結，但係忍到的話，時間係會沖淡一切，所謂既鍾意並無你想像中咁根心替顧。<br />\n<br />\n你依家響佢身邊無非都係最後既掙扎，始終唔會得到永恆，就算你唔離開佢，終有一日佢都會間接疏遠你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d77cab060111799f1d79b9d9083008e4df1e75","tid":1138710,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53599590342d6ccfe530b4faa465f45986c108ed","tid":1138710,"uid":141237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:09:08.000Z","msg":"極速死心就係即刻斷絕聯繫，del records<br />\ndel晒所有可以contact到既途徑。<br />\n<br />\n依段時間，你會好糾結，但係忍到的話，時間係會沖淡一